task.summary:
Remove autogenerated jOOQ files for obsolete routines
Deleted unused autogenerated jOOQ classes related to cricket batting records due to redundancy or lack of use. This cleanup reduces clutter and ensures the repository doesn't contain unnecessary files.

Refactor file handling and remove unused utility.
Streamlined file handling across methods with proper resource management using `.use`. Removed the unused `Random.kt` helper to clean up unused code. Modified the `PlayersmatchesRecord` class for additional attributes related to substitutes.

Delete jOOQ-generated routine files.
Removed autogenerated files related to batting career records, era index, and individual statistics routines. These files are likely no longer needed or replaced by updated implementations.
